|17| Elijah was a man of like feeling [or ^similar nature^] to us, and in
prayer he prayed ^for it^ not to rain, and it ^did^ not rain on the earth ^for^
three years and six months.

# 1 Kings 17:1
# Elijah Announces a Great Drought - Now Elijah the Tishbite, from Tishbe in
